---
// GuaranteeSection - The Performance Guarantee: pay-per-appointment trial campaign
---

<section id="guarantee" class="guarantee-section noise-bg">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="guarantee-card">
      <div class="card-glow"></div>

      <div class="card-content">
        <div class="shield-wrap">
          <iconify-icon icon="lucide:shield-check" class="shield-icon"></iconify-icon>
        </div>

        <h2>Try It Completely Risk-Free</h2>

        <p class="guarantee-text">
          You only pay for real people who show up on your calendar. We promise <span class="green-text">30 qualified consults</span> in 30 days. If we don't deliver, you get a refund for every one we missed. Simple as that.
        </p>

        <div class="guarantee-grid">
          <div class="guarantee-item">
            <iconify-icon icon="lucide:check-circle" class="guarantee-check"></iconify-icon>
            <div>
              <p class="guarantee-title">No Commitment Upfront</p>
              <p class="guarantee-desc">You see real people walking through your doors before you decide to keep going.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="guarantee-item">
            <iconify-icon icon="lucide:check-circle" class="guarantee-check"></iconify-icon>
            <div>
              <p class="guarantee-title">We Only Win When You Win</p>
              <p class="guarantee-desc">If we don't deliver real consults, we don't get paid. Our skin is in the game.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="guarantee-item">
            <iconify-icon icon="lucide:check-circle" class="guarantee-check"></iconify-icon>
            <div>
              <p class="guarantee-title">Zero Work for Your Team</p>
              <p class="guarantee-desc">We handle the outreach, the ads, and every follow-up. Your team just shows up and closes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .guarantee-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--page-bg);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .guarantee-section { padding: 8rem 0; }
  }

  .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 72rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .container { padding: 0 2rem; }
  }

  .guarantee-card {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--guarantee-gradient);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-border);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) { .guarantee-card { padding: 3rem; } }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .guarantee-card { padding: 4rem; } }

  .card-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; right: 0;
    width: 24rem; height: 24rem;
    background: var(--accent-bg);
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(80px);
    transform: translate(50%, -50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .card-content {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .shield-wrap {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 5rem; height: 5rem;
    background: var(--accent-bg-strong);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .shield-icon { color: var(--accent); font-size: 2.5rem; }

  .card-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display, 'Clash Grotesk', sans-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .guarantee-text {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 42rem;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .green-text { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }

  .guarantee-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    text-align: left;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .guarantee-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
  }

  .guarantee-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .guarantee-check {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.125rem;
  }

  .guarantee-title {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .guarantee-desc {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>
